## Procedural Contract

> One state = one dispatch. The orchestrator dispatches the owner agent once with the state's skills loaded. Each review tier is a separate dispatch with a separate flowr transition between them. Never combine multiple states into one dispatch. The todo list is the execution contract — every item marked before moving on.

