## Anchor Checklist (FAA AC 120-71b)

Before exiting this state, confirm each item aloud:

- [ ] **Dispatch completed:** Exactly one agent dispatch happened with exactly the skills listed above.
- [ ] **Single-state scope:** No work from adjacent states was performed during this dispatch.
- [ ] **Flowr next checked:** `flowr next --session` (or `flowr next <flow> <state>`) ran and available transitions are known.
- [ ] **Transition executed:** `flowr transition <trigger> --session` (or `flowr transition <flow> <state> <trigger>`) ran successfully.
- [ ] **Todo rewritten:** New todo list generated from the next state's metadata via `flowr check --session`.
- [ ] **No state skipped:** Every item above this anchor is marked `[X]`. If any are incomplete, stop and complete them before transitioning.
